        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Tell colloquial time using vor, nach, halb, and Viertel without the word Uhr, and read halb + next hour for half past (e.g., halb acht = 7:30).",
            "For separable-prefix verbs (ab-, an-, auf-, aus-, ein-, mit-, etc.), place the conjugated stem in second position and move the prefix to the end of the clause.",
            "Do not separate inseparable-prefix verbs (be-, ent-, er-, ge-, miss-, ver-, zer-)."
        ],
